This software is distributed through the Envato Marketplace and is
licensed under the Envato Market Item License that you accept when you
purchase the item.

Two license tiers are available:

  • Regular License — use in a single end product, accessed by you or
    one client; the end product cannot be sold to others. Suitable for
    using the template inside an internal CRM, or for one client
    project.

  • Extended License — use in a single end product, accessed by you or
    one client; the end product can be sold to multiple end users.
    Suitable for SaaS where end users pay to access the product.

For the full and authoritative license text, see the URLs that Envato
publishes alongside your purchase:

  Regular:  https://themeforest.net/licenses/standard
  Extended: https://themeforest.net/licenses/extended

Open-source dependencies (Next.js, React, Tailwind, Supabase client,
googleapis, next-intl, etc.) remain under their own licenses, which
ship with their packages in `node_modules/`.

If you have not purchased this item through Envato, you do not have a
